{
  "stem": "1826.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's a long way, a long way.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the last-- the last few days, somebody came in and told these-- the sisters, you know, that the Germans are going to evacuate all men, all men, regardless of who it is, all men.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And since I was a man, then what should we do?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They'll come.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then, again, [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Maria ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Nikichna ?] knew somebody who lived-- among the mountains-- far away, the mountains.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they asked me to go there, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was already getting dark.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And on the way, a German officer stopped me, and asked me where is the [?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Rosa ?] factory, where-- of tobacco somehow how are there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he had to pick me up to ask me where this factory is.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But I somehow-- so I managed not to give myself away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I came to this place, to this guy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "His name was [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Kluge. ?] And there were already about 40 men-- Ukrainian-- from town.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Because they didn't want to be evacuated to a German labor camp [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they're expecting to.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And that-- and taht night, we already heard the Russian-- you know, the Russian voices, and the shooting everything.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And the Russians were-- were throwing some leaflets, leaflets in German, in German to demoralize the German soldiers, you know.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And one of these-- they brought in one of this leaflet, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I was so stupid to take this leaflet.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And there are 40 Ukrainian men to translate it to them, this leaflet.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "This was the most stupid thing one can do.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And-- but the reaction was not.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Stupid, because nobody of these Ukrainian knew the Germans would be able to translate a leaflet.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The leaflets were in German.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was for the German soldiers.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
